programme.title: Galaksi Ep6
programme.desc: Sebuah program majalah yang membawa penonton meneroka rahsia alam semesta dari aspek sains, teknologi dan sejarah. Setiap episod mengandungi 3 segmen iaitu Tajuk Utama, Tahukah Anda (membawa trivia dan fakta menarik) dan Eksperimen (yang boleh dilakukan di rumah). Episod kali ini Hos Amirul Hazim, membawa penonton meneroka misteri Batuan Angkasa. Penonton akan mengenali jenis-jenis asteroid dan meteor serta memahami risiko ancamannya terhadap Bumi. Segmen Tahukah Anda akan mengupas fakta menarik tentang Cincin Batuan di Planet Zuhal. Dalam segmen Eksperimen, penonton diajar cara mensimulasikan kesan hentaman asteroid ke atas permukaan planet dan bulan.

programme.title: Widuri: Hatimu Aisyah Ep18
programme.desc: Aisyah dibesarkan dengan adat Melayu dan pantang larang. Ketika anak-anak dan suaminya mengamalkan cara hidup moden, timbul konflik keluarga. Akhirnya, Aisyah sedar bahawa kasih sayang lebih penting daripada mematuhi adat lama. Doktor Firdaus datang sekali lagi melamar Wardina. Pinangannya ditolak. Doktor Firdaus tidak menghiraukan isterinya, Rozana. Ibu Firdaus marah dengan kelakuan Doktor Firdaus. Pelakon: Rosnah Johari, Bohari Ibrahim, Mia Nasir, Sarah Daud, Jaslin Puasa, Ahmad Adly Sofwan, Muhammad Razien Hakim, Nur Diana Sri Tun Teja, Mohammad Yusof Azizan, dan Habeeb Rasely.

programme.desc: Pewaris legasi memaparkan proses penyambungan ilmu kraf daripada seorang guru kepada murid yang akan meneruskan legasi yang kian luput ditelan zaman. Saksikan pengusaha Anyaman Rotan, Empin Galing menurunkan ilmu dan legasi pembuatan Angklung kepada anaknya, Khatizah Binti Empin dalam usaha mengekalkan tradisi dan warisan.

programme.title: Telemovie: Lembu Jasni Petola Kasim
programme.desc: Jasni dan Kassim merupakan sahabat baik. Jasni sentiasa menghulurkan bantuan kepada Kassim tidak kira tenaga, wang atau hartanya. Kassim pula terus mengambil kesempatan di atas kebaikan Jasni. Ini menyebabkan ibu dan isteri Jasni marah dengan sikap Kassim. Ibu dan isteri Jasni cuba merancang sesuatu bagi mengajar Kassim agar tidak mengambil kesempatan di atas kebaikan Jasni. Pelakon: Fikree Bakar, Nisha Dir, Isma Aizal Yusof, Yatt Hamzah dan Wan Maimunah.

programme.title: TV1 Kids: Team Curios Ep24
programme.desc: Siri animasi mengisahkan Quincy, seorang kanak-kanak lelaki yang mempunyai rasa ingin tahu dan naluri keadilan yang tinggi. Quincy juga merupakan ketua kepada Pasukan Q yang turut dianggotai kucingnya, Biltz yang memahami Bahasa makhluk asing. AL sebuah robot yang sopan dan Puteri Deirdeseorang makhluk asing yang terdampar di bumi. Kesemua mereka mempunyai lencana khas yang memberikan kuasa luar biasa untuk menyelesaikan masalah di kawasan kejiranan mereka.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: Keringat Firdausi Ep2
programme.desc: Faridah dan Ahmad yang berhadapan dengan cabaran apabila menyedari anak mereka, Haziq, mengalami autisme akibat tiada tindak balas komunikasi. Faridah bergelut untuk menerima kenyataan ini, manakala Ahmad berusaha untuk menyokong keluarga. Kisah ini menyoroti perjuangan mereka dalam mencari pemahaman dan penerimaan terhadap keadaan Haziq. Episod kali ini Faridah berhenti kerja dan bersama Aiman, memberi sepenuh perhatian menjaga Haziq. Dengan penuh kesabaran mereka membawa Haziq berulang alik berjumpa dengan doktor pakar bagi menjalani rawatan terapi khas. Namun, Aiman mula rasa putus asa.Pelakon: Izreen Azminda, Zamarul Hisham, Aiman Badrol, Izzy Reef, Jay Nazif, Hafidz Roshdi, Hanna Aqeela, Mak Wan, Bahari Ibrahim, Scha Elinnea.

programme.title: Galaksi Ep13
programme.desc: Sebuah program majalah yang membawa penonton meneroka rahsia alam semesta dari aspek sains, teknologi dan sejarah. Menampilkan hos Amirul Hazim. Episod kali ini Hos Amirul Hazim, meneroka Teknologi Angkasa, yang melibatkan sistem dan peralatan seperti roket, satelit, dan stesen angkasa untuk penerokaan angkasa lepas. Dalam segmen Tahukah Anda, penonton akan mengetahui bahawa buang angin di angkasa boleh meningkatkan risiko kebakaran bagi angkasawan. Segmen Eksperimen pula mengajar cara menghasilkan Roket Air untuk memahami konsep tujahan dengan lebih jelas.

Goyang badan papanya namun tidak bergerak. Rahul makin kuat kejut papanya. Raziq tak bergerak jugak. Rahul susah hati dan kejutkan lagi namun tidak bangun juga lalu dia menjerit memanggil nendanya.

programme.title: Religious Clip S67 Ep12

programme.title: Di Sisimu Aku Ep11
programme.desc: Zamir dan Aman bergegas ke balai polis untuk bawak Qeena balik. Qeena menerpa kepada Aman di belakang Zamir secara spontan. Zamir memahami, hati Qeena untuk Aman. Bukan untuknya. Zamir sangat kecewa dan sedih.

programme.title: Bintang Hatiku Ep3
programme.desc: Nirda kejutkan Rahul sambil panggil dan memandang Hanani yang buat bodoh. Tiba-tiba Rahul bangun duduk dan menggoyankan kepalanya macam nak sedarkan diri. Nirda pelik dan Hanani hanya tersenyum sinis kerana tahu Rahul hanya berpura pengsan. programme.title: Mek Gyver Ep6

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep02
programme.desc: 2013, Rian sebagai pelajar universiti dan Afeeq yang dianggap idaman ramai, tetapi Rian hanya melihat Afeeq sebagai abang. Pada 2018, selepas Afeeq pulang dari Australia, dia mula mengusik Rian dengan kata-kata yang penuh makna, namun Rian menganggapnya sebagai gurauan. Adif, yang secara rahsia mengunjungi hospital mental banyak berkongsi cerita dengan sepupunya, Sham. Adif buat keputusan melamar Rian tetapi kemudian tidak hiraukan Rian, membuat Rian terasa seperti dimain mainkan. Adif marah apabila melihat Rian mesra dengan Afeeq pula, menyebabkan berlaku pertengkaran. Rian menjelaskan hubungannya dengan Afeeq, sementara Adif memujuk Rian dan menyatakan hasratnya untuk meminang, tetapi Rian curiga dengan niat Adif.

programme.title: Madu Murni
programme.desc: Cerita berpusat pada Mustaqim (Ammar Zoni), seorang bekas guru mengaji yang kini bekerja sebagai penagih hutang untuk mendapatkan pendapatan yang lebih banyak. Namun, isterinya, Murni (Irish Bella), tidak menyetujui pekerjaan Mustaqim dan enggan menerima wang yang diperolehnya kerana bimbang akan risiko di dunia akhirat.

programme.title: Nasi Kerabu Untuk Che Abe Ep03
programme.desc: Ibu shira dapat rasakan Shira dilamun cinta kerana sanggup cuba makan budu. Cuti pertengahan semester bermula dan Faizul balik ke Kelantan. Setibanya di rumah dia terkejut Mek Yan Mek Yan marah Atikah teruk sebab difitnah orang kampung. Faizul meminta Mek Yan izinkan sahaja Atikah berkahwin dengan Mat Yie. Faizul dapat panggilan, teruja sangat apabila tahu Shira dekat Kota Bahru. Shira sanggup tipu semua orang konon ada urusan bisnes semata-mata mahu jumpa Faizul. Mereka seronok luangkan masa bersama dan perasaan mereka semakin mendalam. Faizul jemput shira ke rumahnya. Mek Yan bimbang Shira moden tak bertudung berbanding Pia, anak Tok Imam yang dia mahu jodohkan dengan Faizul.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep02
programme.desc: Atas nasihat rakannya, Rojak (Tanta Ginting), Mustaqim memutuskan untuk berkahwin lagi dengan Yati (Aulia Sarah). Filem ini mengisahkan bagaimana Mustaqim cuba mengimbangi kehidupan dengan dua isteri dan pelbagai cabaran yang dihadapinya

programme.title: Suamiku Mr Blind S1 Ep17
programme.desc: 6 BULAN KEMUDIAN.Sebaik sahaja Aidil sampai ke lapangan terbang, dia terus menghubungi Ain dan mengarahkan Ain untuk berjumpa dengannya. Selesai sahaja tugasnya sebagai cikgu pada hari itu, Ain terkejut apabila mendapat panggilan daripada suaminya itu. Dia tertanya-tanya kenapa Aidil berjumpanya. Disebabkan Ain tidak memandu, Cikgu Solehin yang kebetulan ingin balik, meminta untuk menghantar Ain ke stesen LRT yang berdekatan. Ain tidak membantah kerana ternyata selain seorang yang baik, cikgu Solehin juga sebenarnya menaruh hati pada Ain. Dalam pada itu, Aidil masih pura-pura buta. Bermulalah episode Ain diperhambakan oleh suaminya sendiri.

programme.title: Pengantin 100 Hari Ep08
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Yasmin memecat suaminya sendiri dari CEO syarikat setelah mengetahui wang sebanyak RM250 ribu diberi sebagai gantirugi kepada Sofia apabila anaknya Amar menceraikannya. Amar pula sengaja melakukan provokasi supaya Sofia bencikan dirinya kerana dia tidak lagi mampu memberi zuriat kepada Sofia. Amar juga merahsiakan tersebut dari Erina. Sofia masih tinggal dengan rakannya Farah, masih merahsiakan perceraiannya dari keluarga. Satu hari, tiba-tiba Sofia jatuh pengsan. Beliau disahkan hamil hasil perhubungan dengan Amar semasa sebelum diceraikan. Farah terpaksa menghubungi Kak Warda dan Iqbal memaklumkan hal kesihatan Sofia. Semasa Sofia balik bersama Kak Warda dan Iqbal, berita perceraiannya baharu diketahui oleh ibunya. Terkejut dengan berita tersebut ibunya jatuh pengsan dan meninggal dunia. Sofia sangat menyesal dengan kejadian tersebut.

programme.desc: Rian kasihan dan tidak faham mengapa Adif tidak terus terang yang Adif terpaksa jaga Adelia yang ada masalah mental selepas mak ayah Adif meninggal dunia kemalangan. Ia buatkan Rian semakin menyayangi Adif. Pada 2010, Adif belajar di London dan Adelia yang bercita-cita jadi model. Pada 2014, Adif merasa Adelia telah berubah sikap jadi murung dan jauhkan diri. Sementara itu, Rania merancang menjual butik dan meminta Rian merahsiakannya. Rian juga menghadapi masalah dengan Adif yang semakin menjauhkan diri dari keluarganya.

programme.desc: Cikgu Solehin tidak habis-habis cuba memancing Ain. Dia selalu menggunakan khidmat tidak bertauliah Wahida untuk membantunya. Wahida ialah seorang guru yang merangkap sahabat Ain. Sejak-sejak melihat Ain yang sangat cantik dan ayu, Aidil menjadi serba tak kena duduk di rumah. Sebab itulah dia mula belajar menjadi spy dan mengintip isterinya sendiri. Wahida yang langsung tidak tahu Ain sudah berpunya, sentiasa membantu Cikgu Solehin mendapatkan Ain. Alangkah kecilnya dunia apabila Ain dapat tahu Kakak Wahida adalah Wani yang rupanya kekasih Ryan. Ryan dan Wani mengalami kemalangan teruk. Ketika itulah, dia berjumpa dengan Puan Maimon yang memohon seribu kemaafan atas apa yang terjadi kepadanya. Aidil amat marah apabila melihat Ain dan Solehin bagaikan pasangan bercinta.

programme.title: Pengantin 100 Hari Ep09
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Amar ditumbuk oleh Iqbal semasa bersama isterinya Erina, Iqbal dituduh penyebab kematian ibunya yang terkejut apabila mendengar Sofia diceraikan oleh Amar. Amar membayar wang gantirugi kepada Erina apabila perkahwinan mereka hampir genap 100 hari dan Erina akan dicerai seperti dijanjikan. Sofia menggunakan sebahagian wang gantirugi pemberian Amar membeli sebuah kedai untuk memulakan perniagaan butik pakaian demi masa depan anak dalam kandungannya. Sofia juga menuntut baki gantirugi sebanyak RM250 ribu dibayar segera. Amar akhirnya menceraikan Erina pada hari ke 100 selepas perkahwinan mereka. Amar mengaku kepada Sofia dia tidak dapat memberi zuriat akibat kemalangan tempoh hari. Erina memahami keadaan tersebut tetapi merasa terkilan apabila Amar menceraikan Sofia. Datuk Fahmi (datuk Sofia) terlalu marah dan cuba menembak Amar sebaik sahaja diketahui cucunya dicerai oleh Amar.

Selepas persidangan perceraian, Abi dan Ken bertemu di sebuah warung kopi dan mula berkongsi cerita tentang kehidupan mereka. Mereka berdua merasa bahawa perceraian adalah titik terendah dalam hidup mereka, tetapi pemilik warung kopi memberi mereka perspektif baru bahawa menjadi duda bukanlah akhir segalanya.

programme.title: Nasi Kerabu Untuk Che Abe Ep05
programme.desc: Majlis pernikahan Shira dan Faizul akhirnya berlangsung. Faizul terlepas malam pertama sebab Datuk Badrul ajak Faizul bersembang tentang nak pasarkan bisnes budu Mek Yan. Pagi itu, selepas subuh berjemaah, Faizul pegang tangan Shira dan cakap dia sayang Shira dan berjanji akan susah senang bersama. Siang itu, Faizul ambil barang-barangnya di rumah sewa. Shira perasan Arman sedikit dingin. Arman sebenarnya jauh hati sebab dalam diam dia sukakan Shira. Minggu berikutnya, mereka balik ke Kelantan. Shira sesuaikan diri pakai juga baju sopan. Mek Yan pesan pada Shira untuk masak nasi kerabu sebab itu kegemaran Faizul. Shira mati akal sebab tak pernah masak nasi kerabu. Namun pagi subuh, Shira terkejut bila melihat nasi kerabutelah pun terhidang di atas meja.

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S13 Ep08
programme.desc: Dengan bajet RM10,Naem tukang masak Dapur Bujang akan menyediakan dua jenis hidangan masakan harian yang senang, sedap dan sihat.

programme.title: Pengantin 100 Hari Ep09
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Amar ditumbuk oleh Iqbal semasa bersama isterinya Erina, Iqbal dituduh penyebab kematian ibunya yang terkejut apabila mendengar Sofia diceraikan oleh Amar. Amar membayar wang gantirugi kepada Erina apabila perkahwinan mereka hampir genap 100 hari dan Erina akan dicerai seperti dijanjikan. Sofia menggunakan sebahagian wang gantirugi pemberian Amar membeli sebuah kedai untuk memulakan perniagaan butik pakaian demi masa depan anak dalam kandungannya. Sofia juga menuntut baki gantirugi sebanyak RM250 ribu dibayar segera. Amar akhirnya menceraikan Erina pada hari ke 100 selepas perkahwinan mereka. Amar mengaku kepada Sofia dia tidak dapat memberi zuriat akibat kemalangan tempoh hari. Erina memahami keadaan tersebut tetapi merasa terkilan apabila Amar menceraikan Sofia. Datuk Fahmi (datuk Sofia) terlalu marah dan cuba menembak Amar sebaik sahaja diketahui cucunya dicerai oleh Amar.

programme.title: Trend Setter S4 Ep05
programme.desc: Episod ini jom kita usha kedai iaitu Mimpi Kita dan bersembang bersama Nana Mahazan dalam Gaya dan Kerjaya.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep08
programme.desc: Pada tahun 2016, Adif ditemuduga oleh Idris untuk jawatan peguam syarikat,. Adif gembira diterima kerja. Idris memuji Adif dalam mesyuarat dan berkongsi tentang anaknya, Rian, yang bakal graduasi. Pada 2017, Adif menghadiri majlis perkahwinan Hafiz iaitu saudara mara Rian. Adif kemudian meyakinkan Ahli Lembaga tentang perubahan syarikat dan meminta , mendesak dris menandatangani dokumen pemindahan harta, dengan syarat Adif akan tidak menyakiti Rian. Ia kejutan besat buat Idris. Selepas menandatangani dokumen sebagai Penaung, Adif merasa dendamnya terbalas dengan meletakkan gambar keluarganya di pejabat Idris.

programme.title: Hanya Kawan
programme.desc: Hans dan Ella merupakan pasangan kekasih yang masing-masing memasang impian untuk menjadi pelakon dan penyanyi yang berjaya suatu hari nanti. Ella yang ditemui seorang penerbit lagu, Michael Nasir mula mencapai kejayaan terlebih dahulu. Percaya akan kebolehan Ella, dia ditawarkan untuk menyertai syarikat rakamannya. Hubungan antara Hans dan Ella mula menghadapi masalah apabila Ella kelihatan semakin rapat dengan Michael dan makin berjaya manakala Hnas masih mencari-cari arah sebagai seorang pelakon.

programme.title: Alahai Cucu Atuk
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ujang yang tinggal bersama datuk setelah bapanya meninggal dunia. Ujang ingin berkahwin dengan Milah. Namun, dia malas bekerja dan hanya mengharapkan harta datuknya sahaja. Pada suatu hari, datuk Ujang menyatakan bahawa dia akan berkahwin dengan seseorang. Ujang kecewa apabila orang yang ingin dinikahi datuknya itu adalah Milah. Dengan hati yang luka, Ujang ingin membuang sifat malasnya dan menjadi seorang lelaki yang lebih baik.

programme.title: Mr Cinderella
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Puteri Megawati, puteri mahkota negara Inderapuri yang mengalami kecederaan dalam satu kemalangan jalanraya telah diselamatkan oleh Hakimi. Semasa meninggalkan tempat kemalangan itu, Hakimi secara tidak sengaja tercicir sebelah kasut yang dipinjam daripada sahabatnya, Kumin. Oleh kerana berasa terhutang budi kepada penyelamatnya, Puteri Megawati meminta pertolongan seorang wartawan untuk mencari Mr Cinderella yang menyelamatkannya dengan ganjaran lumayan.

programme.title: Sejati
programme.desc: Bani, seorang lepasan universiti telah tercedera dalam satu perlumbaan motosikal haram. Semasa mendapat rawatan di hospital, doktor mendapati Bani sedang menghidap penyakit kanser paru-paru yang serius. Dia ke Cameron Highlands untuk berehat dan di situ dia bertemu dengan Haryati yang menghidap penyakit leukimia lalu saling jatuh cinta.

programme.title: Arbaie Bujang Kembali
programme.desc: Semasa isterinya bersalin anak ketiga, Arbaie mengambil kesempatan untuk keluar berfoya-foya dengan rakan-rakannya, Mat Nor dan Ajmain. Arbaie kemudiannya jatuh cinta dengan seorang wanita bernama Nab. Untuk mengelakkan kegiatannya terbongkar, Arbaie mencari helah untuk menghantar isterinya pulang ke kampung. Perbuatan Arbaie itu telah menimbulkan pelbagai masalah kepada dirinya di kemudian hari.

programme.title: Siksa
programme.desc: Seorang gadis bernama Aniza sering menyanyi di majlis-majlis perkahwinan di kampung itu. Aniza mempunyai seorang kekasih bernama Jalal yang sering menjadi pasangan duetnya semasa menyanyi. Aniza berasa kecewa setelah dia mengetahui rupa-rupanya Jalal adalah seorang kaki judi. Setelah dipujuk, Aniza bersetuju untuk berkahwin dengan Jalal yang berjanji tidak akan berjudi lagi. Namun, setelah beberapa tahun mereka berkahwin Jalal masih tidak dapat meninggalkan tabiatnya yang gemar berjudi sehingga membuatkan rumah tangganya dengan Aniza retak akibat banyak hutang.

programme.title: Mr Cinderella 2
programme.desc: Hakimi kini menjadi CEO di syarikat Megapuri Bhd yang dimiliki oleh Puteri Megawati. Oleh sebab tidak dapat membiasakan diri dengan kehidupan barunya, Hakimi bertindak dengan meletakkan jawatan dan perkara ini merisaukan Puteri Megawati. Dalam masa yang sama, seorang wanita bernama Anisah jatuh hati kepada Hakimi. Dia menawarkan pekerjaan kepada Hakimi di syarikatnya dan pelbagai konflik berlaku di antara Hakimi, Puteri Megawati dan Anisah.

programme.title: Man on the Edge
programme.desc: On the eve of the 1997 handover, violence is rampant with triad forces causing chaos in Hong Kong. The triad gang leader assigns his right-hand man Ah Lok to take charge of the drug trafficking business. However, Ah Lok turns out to be an undercover police officer who unveils a shocking political conspiracy during the investigation.

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: This is a love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy and is the first Bollywood movie to be made in Hong Kong. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races. The movie also combines tears, joy and laughter with song and dance.

programme.title: The Moon Thieves
programme.desc: A crooked watch dealer assembles a daring crew - a thief, an explosive expert, a lock breaker and a watch connoisseur - to steal three luxury watches in Tokyo. Their mission takes an unexpected turn when they discover the legendary 'Moonwatch.' Pursued by the yakuza, the team must unite to navigate the chaos and pull off their high-stakes heist.

programme.title: Wu Kong
programme.desc: Set 500 years before the Monkey King Wu Kong wreaks havoc in the heavenly kingdom, the movie tells the story of how Wu Kong who, unwilling to bow to his own destiny, sets out to rebel against the gods.

programme.title: Dummy Mommy, without a Baby
programme.desc: Fong Lai Kuen works at an advertising agency but is about to be sacked by her boss after offending him. She pretends to be pregnant so that the company cannot fire her, according to the labour law. Since then, Fong receives much care and love from her colleagues and begins to feel guilty about her lie as things develop out of her expectations.

programme.title: Red Line
programme.desc: A former professional car racer, Le falls into despair after causing his brother's death in a car race, until he meets female doctor Hui and becomes an ambulance driver who vows to save lives with speed. Meanwhile, the truth about his brothers accident emerges with the investigation of Le's three good friends...

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: Detrimental
programme.desc: You Ji Ren is a blind man who works at a factory in an outlying island. When the factory is cut off from the outside world by a hurricane one day, a monster appears and turns whoever sees it into black shadows. As You cannot see the monster, he is able to help other coworkers leave safely and fight to kill the monster!

programme.title: First Love the Litter on the Breeze
programme.desc: This movie is the directorial debut of actor Eric Kot for Wong Kar Wai. Eric features the topic of first love in his first movie: a sleepwalker guided through the night by a lonely admirer is bizarre yet romantic, while a married grocer facing the vengeful first love that he once rejected is heartbreaking.

programme.title: Fierce Cop
programme.desc: To save his son who has been kidnapped by human traffickers, police officer Zhang relentlessly hunts them down and accidentally finds himself implicated in a major child abduction case. In the process, he teams up with a mysterious lady to crack the international crime syndicate and rescue his son.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau II
programme.desc: Mark, the chief accountant of a money-laundering syndicate, has stolen US$15 billion from the fund and absconded to Thailand with his daughter. Interpol agent Lok seeks help from Ken, the God of Gamblers, to capture the syndicates mastermind. As they search for Mark to testify in the case, Ken reunites with the love of his life

programme.title: Wu Xia
programme.desc: Martial artist Liu hides his identity and lives in a remote village with his wife Ah Yu and their two sons, but somehow gets embroiled in a bizarre murder case. Constable Xu is a kung fu fanatic, whose curiosity forces Liu into a death duel with the Sect Leader of the 72 Demons, and puts Lius family and homeland in a great danger...

programme.title: Dad, I'm Sorry
programme.desc: Ba Sang lives in a poor district in Saigon and his son Woan is a Youtuber earning considerable income. Woan wants his father to enjoy retirement, so he is mad at him for being a meddler and making unnecessary sacrifices. This has created conflicts between the two generations and leads to a crisis in the father and son relationship.

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find the-one?

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: This is a story about two brothers. The younger brother is a drug lord while the elder brother Zhong is a police officer in the Narcotics Bureau. Both are involved in a drug cartels turf battle and during an escort mission, Zhong discovers his brothers hidden identity. This leads to an endless battle between good and evil.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 2
programme.desc: In this sequel, Zhang Wu Ji successfully rescued the Six Major sects at Dadu. Nevertheless, the quest for the Dragon Sabre continues as Wu Ji and his three girlfriends set sail for Ice Fire Island. After a series of vicious fights, they finally unveil the secret behind the Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre.

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: A commercial director Peggy shoots an ad on a deserted island while some mysterious men with the treasure map are also there to hunt for the hidden Ming Dynasty treasures. However, the map is stolen by Star who lives on the island. Star and Peggy unveil the hidden treasures but end up being chased by the mysterious men

programme.title: Kowloon Walled City
programme.desc: Neng was a street fighter in Northeast China but decides to start a new life in Hong Kongs Kowloon Walled City. Unfortunately, he is implicated in the fights and conspiracies among the triad forces. When his good friend is hunted down by the triad, Neng must team up with the residents of Kowloon Walled City to fight back and save his friend.

programme.title: The Movie Emperor
programme.desc: Hong Kong megastar Lau Wai Chi aspires to win a film award. He teams up with director Lin Hao to make a film about rural China so as to win at the international film festival, and experiences local village life for the farmers role. This ends up in a series of hilarious events instead.

programme.title: July Rhapsody
programme.desc: A 40-year-old high school teacher is in midlife crisis, his marriage is on the rocks and he is involved in a taboo romance with a female student who has a crush on him. Meanwhile, his wife is off to care for her dying ex-lover who shares a complicated history with the couple...

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Distinction
programme.desc: A music teacher in a special needs school, an underachiever from an elite school, and a rebellious teenager with a handicapped brother take part in a campus musical for various reasons. Little did they know that this turns out to be a journey of self-discovery.

programme.title: Tainted Love
programme.desc: Office lady Zhou Ran falls victim to an online dating love scam and is cheated of 550,000 yuan. Following faint clues left by the scammer, Zhou Ran comes to a small coastal town and encounters two young men. She gradually discovers that these two men have hidden the clues of the scam, and sets out on her revenge plan.

programme.title: The Phantom Lover
programme.desc: In 1926 China, Sung, a talented singer, is deeply in love with To, a sweet innocent girl from a wealthy family. Their love evokes strong disapproval from To's father and bitter jealousy from her designated fiance, a young man chosen by her family. It is a story about a singer and a wealthy girl battling to be together in a traditional community.

programme.title: Bodyguards and Assassins
programme.desc: On 15 October 1906, Chinese revolutionary leader Sun Yat Sen returned to Hong Kong to stage another overthrow of the Qing dynasty. Businessman Lee and Chinese Dailys Chief Chan arrange for five bodyguards to protect Mr Sun - these are all extraordinary fighters who are ready and up for fierce battles against the Qing assassination army.

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Back Home
programme.desc: Wing has been able to see ghosts since young. When his mothers suicide attempt forces him to return to Hong Kong and the home he ran away from, he discovers that the horrific visions that once haunted him have become worse. Caught between the living and the dead, Wing must bring the truth to light to be free.

programme.title: Fallen Angels
programme.desc: The funkier cousin to Chungking Express, director Wong Kar Wai looks at five fallen angels who suffer love and loss amidst the crime and chaos of Hong Kongs neon nights in this movie. Karen Mok won Best Supporting Actress in the 15th Hong Kong Film Awards for her remarkable role as a broken-hearted party girl.

programme.title: The White Storm 2: Drug Lords
programme.desc: In this epic action-thriller starring Andy Lau and Louis Koo, the two award-winning best actors star on opposing sides of a drug war. As a bounty of $100 million Hong Kong dollars is made to hunt down the biggest drug dealer in the city, Hong Kong becomes the battleground for the fight between good and evil.

programme.title: Have Sword Will Travel
programme.desc: When the head of a manor loses his kung fu skills, he enlists his nephew and his fianc to help escort gold to the capital. The duo run into a mysterious knight along the way and they join hands to prevent bandits from stealing the gold.

programme.title: The Champion
programme.desc: After years in prison, Lu Hu returns home to find himself set up by his ruthless brother Piao, who has taken over the family coal mine business and imprisoned their sister. Hu takes down Piao and saves his sister but their coal mine falls into the hands of a Japanese gang, which Hu and his sister must fight in order to get it back.

programme.title: Twelve Deadly Coins
programme.desc: When Qiao Miao is about to kill the bandit whom he just met, he is attracted by her beauty and they quickly fall in love. The two later discover the blood feud between the owner of the unique weapon - Twelve Deadly Coins and the old master who controls the bandit...

programme.title: When the Clouds Roll By
programme.desc: Su is a schizophrenic who refuses to believe that her pilot lover is killed in a plane crash and makes up stories to deal with things. She runs into an old classmate Lai, who is also a doctor one day, and he finds ways to treat her illness. Su slowly recovers and accepts the reality, as well as her newfound love.

programme.title: One Way Only
programme.desc: Danny is a motorbike workshop owner, once was a renowned motorcycle racer, but were seriously injured in an illegal race. Mai, student of Danny, wins a race in Macau under Danny's help. However, because of money and honour, Mai joins illegal races. After knowing this, Li persuades Mai to stop illegal races, but Mai seems cannot find his way out

programme.title: Dawn will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parents consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her

programme.title: To Kill a Mastermind
programme.desc: A ruthless crime syndicate, Qi Sha clan, which is controlled by seven chiefs is terrorizing China. The Imperial Court orders Minister Yang to bring them down by sending undercovers to the clan and disintegrating them from the inside. As more internal conflicts occur, will the masterminds of the clan find out who are the spys?

programme.title: Lover's Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a mans role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: The Boxer From The Temple
programme.desc: A young monk, The Kid, was expelled from the temple due to his crazy ways. After leaving the temple, he fights a cruel bandit's son and befriends a prostitute. As he fights for justice, his Crazy Lo Han Fist improves with every fight.

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back

programme.title: Hex
programme.desc: This supernatural mystery tells the story of a sickly wife and her maid conspiring to kill her beastly husband, leading to a string of events with spooky twists and turns.

programme.title: The Five Venoms
programme.desc: A dying master dispatches his last pupil to track down five ex-students who are each an expert in his own lethal combat style. He fears they will steal the fortune belonging to their clan and tasks his pupil to prevent their attempt.

programme.title: Man Of Iron
programme.desc: Chou Lian Huan (Chen Kuan Tai) is good at fist fighting in Shanghai. In order to please a hostess named Chen Ju Fang (Ching Li), he is willing to sacrifice everything and fight against the son of the gang leader in Shanghai. However, is Chous action worth it?

programme.title: Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers?
programme.desc: Jenny Hu, Shaw Brothers' gorgeous Chinese-German star, was given her first comedy role in the wild and wacky Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers? Described as "a comedy of belly laughs and chilling murders", it is a unique entry in the Hong Kong theater of the absurd.

programme.title: Kid From Kwangtung
programme.desc: After many years as a respected actor and action choreographer, the Shaw Studio finally gave the dependable and commendable Hsu Hsia a chance to direct his own movies. He didn't waste the opportunity, inviting three other kung-fu designers to help on this fight-filled thriller. Wang Yu, co-star of such classics as Dirty Ho and The Kid With A Tattoo, here takes center stage as a young rascal caught between an anti-Ching Confederation and violent, vengeful Ching troops. But when he discovers that the good guys are led by master martial arts actor Jen Shih-kuan and the bad guys are led by the incredible Huang Cheng-li everyone knows that loads of great kung-fu is in store.

programme.title: The Perfumed Arrow
programme.desc: A charming Huangmei Opera title, this is the story of Fei E, a Generals daughter who grows up fooling everyone that she is a boy, including her two closest schoolmates. When she has to choose one of them to marry, how will Fei E tell them that she is a girl? To complicate matters, a girl who Fei E saves one day only wants to be married to her!

programme.title: Shaolin Hand Lock
programme.desc: Li Cheng Yings father was set up and killed by his old friend Ling Hao. Li, who has learnt Shaolin Hand Lock from his father, is on a mission to avenge his death. He works as an undercover guard at Lings house where he meets his long-lost brother, and the two team up to take revenge for their father against Ling.

programme.title: My Dream Boat
programme.desc: This is a story about the complicated love relationships between a group of young friends who are entangled in a web of love and emotions.

programme.title: The Lady Hermit
programme.desc: The Lady Hermit hides away for years to plot revenge after being defeated by the evil Black Knight. Young swordswoman Tsui Ping is determined to take down Black Knight herself and begs Lady Hermit to teach her martial arts skills. The Black Knight's days are numbered when the Lady Hermit and her protege perfect the technique to take him down.

programme.title: Song Of Orchid Island
programme.desc: Dr. He moves to the remote Lanyu island off the coast of Taiwan to look for his long lost father, and starts to run a clinic curing islanders who are bitten by the fatal red worms there. He meets Ya Lan who works as a nurse in his clinic and falls in love with him. Things get vicious for Dr. He as a jealous islander plots to get rid of him

programme.title: The 36th Chamber of Shaolin
programme.desc: Gordon Liu plays an anti-Manchu rebel who escapes to the Shaolin Temple and learns what it truly takes to become a martial arts master by challenging the 35 Shaolin Kung Fu chambers, eventually creating the 36th chamber himself.

programme.title: Madam White Snake
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai is perfect as Pak Su-cheng, the stunning snake goddess who assumes a womanly form so that she can taste the pleasures of a human life! Pak seduces young scholar, Hsu Hsien when she recognises him as her saviour in another life 1,000 years ago. But when Buddhist monk Fa Hai finds out about the union, the pair is forced to split...

programme.title: King Eagle
programme.desc: A young swordman, King Eagle, unwillingly gets involved in the internal affairs of a powerful clan and becomes their target. He is saved by the female chief of the clan, Lin, and falls in love with her. However, Lins sister is part of all evil plots and betrays her. Even so, Lin begs King Eagle not to harm her sister.

programme.title: Carry on Doctors and Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: The Bride from Hell
programme.desc: A young business man marries a pretty and much sought-after young bride, not knowing that she carries the spirit of a girl raped by her uncle and murdered along with her parents. Justice must be done, and it ain't pretty!

programme.title: Three Sinners
programme.desc: Based on the classic Ming Dynasty novel The Water Margin, Three Sinners is a Huangmei Opera about love, betrayal, murder, and redemption. Starring Hong Kong's premiere movie couple, it is one of the grandest Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musicals in the Shaw Brothers library.

programme.title: Na Cha And The Seven Devils
programme.desc: While stealing one magical peach from a mystic tree in Heaven, Little Na Cha accidentally drops seven others on Earth, which transformed seven different animals into seven devils. Na Cha must hunt the devils down in ten days or his father will be punished by the King of Heaven. Can Na Cha complete his mission?

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: Double Bliss
programme.desc: Dong and Chu plan to get married but their families who are lifelong rivals, disapproved. They decide to fake suicide and eventually get both of their parents to settle their differences and approve the marriage. Concurrently, a record company announces that they will release Dongs songs, leading to double bliss for the couple.

programme.title: The Eight Diagram Pole Fighter
programme.desc: The Yang Generals were ambushed by the enemies and only two of the sons survived. The fifth son of Yangs escapes to Shaolin temple and learns the pole-fighting techniques from the monks, eventually creating his own Eight Diagram Pole Fight and teaming up with the Shaolin monks to avenge his family.

programme.title: Scandal
programme.desc: The roguish scamp Zhen and his best friend Chia collects proof of corruption from the officials in this comedy-drama. After a string of blackmailing, they end up in positions of power, but what is to happen next?

programme.title: The Chinese Boxer
programme.desc: A Japanese karate master and Diao Er, who has been expelled from his martial arts school, return to the school to kill the school master and his disciples. After the massacre, disciple Lei Ming embarks on a vigorous training regime and vows to avenge their deaths. A fatal battle is about to begin

programme.title: The Adulteress
programme.desc: The film is about the drugged, then disgraced wife of a peddler in the waning days of the Ching Dynasty. To make matters worse, shes soon framed for her husbands murder by her rapist, the son of the local magistrate! And even that is not the end of her woes in this emotional suspense

programme.title: The Magnificent Ruffians
programme.desc: A gang of unemployed martial artists seem to have their bad fortunes turned when the head of a local security agency hires them to take out the competition, who their new employer insists is up to no good. However, the men are being played for fools and have to take each other on until the last drop of blood is spilled.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: Zhang and Jins daughter, Peony, are betrothed at birth but Jin objects to the engagement now. Zhang meets a carp spirit that looks exactly like Peony and they fall in love. When Justice Bao is asked by Jin to distinguish Peony from her replica, he decides to quit the case when he witness the true love between Zhang and the carp spirit.
